meanings.definition: Surpassing all others in excellence or greatness.
meanings.sent1: The supereminent chef prepared a delicious meal for the guests.
meanings.sent2: The supereminent mountain peak could be seen from miles away.
meanings.sent3: The supereminent cake was so good that it disappeared in seconds.
meanings.sent4: Her supereminent talent shone brightly on the stage.
meanings.sent5: The supereminent sunset painted the sky in vibrant colors.

meanings.definition: Of the highest rank or quality.
meanings.sent1: The supereminent student always scored the highest in class.
meanings.sent2: The supereminent diamond sparkled in the sunlight.
meanings.sent3: The supereminent car zoomed past all the others on the track.
meanings.sent4: His supereminent leadership skills guided the team to victory.
meanings.sent5: The supereminent performance left the audience in awe.
